            {
              "type": "list",
              "ordered": true,
              "items": [
                "A courier company becomes a business associate when it signs a BAA with a covered entity."
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "list",
              "ordered": true,
              "items": [
                "PHI can include a patient\u2019s address even without medical details attached."
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "list",
              "ordered": true,
              "items": [
                "A courier who uses their personal phone for work deliveries is automatically HIPAA compliant."
